  "title": "Assistant ENGINEER ( CIVIL) cum drafter",
  "description": "<p>A. Main Responsibilities</p>\n<p>1 Responsible for all on-site technical and engineering matters and drafting matters.</p>\n<p>2 Ensure works carried out meet company’s quality standards &amp; contractual requirements.</p>\n<p>3 Involved in project planning, monitoring project progress and schedule.</p>\n<p>Including prepare work plan, schedule, preparation all the related work procedure/method statement, job safety analysis, technical clarification.</p>\n<p>4 To co-ordinate with the client, consultant, sub-contractors on all project aspects and need be, to provide all technical and non-technical resolutions followed by documentation.</p>\n<p>Include attending all progress meeting.</p>\n<p>5 Assisting Project Manager in monthly progress claims and monthly progress reports.</p>\n<p>6 Ensuring supervisors, foremen, workers and sub-con meets client &amp; regulatory work requirements. 7 Ensuring Environmental, Safety and Health practices are carried out at all times.</p>\n<p>8 Other ad-hoc duties assigned from time to time</p>",
